rows.label: tlk70000036_90_msg0001
rows.name:
Hm hm, it's certainly rare to
meet Drivers and their Blades.

rows.label: tlk70000036_90_msg0002
rows.name:
I came here to investigate monsters.
Hah! It's quite the life for an old
lady. Wouldn't trade it for the world.

rows.label: tlk70000036_90_msg0003
rows.name:
You seem like reliable young
tykes. Maybe I'll tell you
about it someday...

rows.label: tlk70000036_90_msg0004
rows.name:
If you want to know more about
this village, though, you'll
have to ask someone else.
